      <mj-section>
        <mj-column width="91%" background-color="#f3f3f3" padding="20px">
          <mj-text align="center">
            <strong>Enhance your workflows with exceptional A3 performance, upgraded speed, reliability, and efficiency.</strong>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-button href="https://www.ricoh.com/" width="300px">
